A garden of dusty peach dahlia flowers in full bloom, let your imagination run wild with our ‘Dusty Peach Embroidered Net Lehenga’ by Lashkaraa. The cropped choli and lehenga have been exquisitely worked with a foliage of thread work, foil and tilla embroideries in shades of peachy pink and silver. The dainty sequin-work between the floral elements gives a wave-like illusion, making the lehenga look balletic and flowy. The overlaid net lehenga has a darker orange hued lining  that makes the  the overall outfit look more vibrant and attractive.

Price: $175 USD | Launching August 28th at 10 AM PST, exclusively at Lashkaraa.com

A fashion faithful choice for your upcoming soiree, our ‘Light Pink Thread Embroidered Gharara Suit’ embodies tradition and modernity.  The highlight of this ensemble is knee-length chust kameez with a worked neckline that feature chevron shaped patterns followed by a cascade of embroidered flowery designs that fall into a heavily worked border, finished with silver tassels. The gharara has a spray of similar floral embellishments with adroitly worked hems. Teamed with a simple laced dupatta, you can create a perfect clutter-free eastern look.

Price: $135 USD | Launching August 28th at 10 AM PST, exclusively at Lashkaraa.com
